"""Need Full Name, Current Age, Desired Retirment Age, Current Level of Retirement Savings, What is the Total Amount of Retirment Savings Is Needed at Retirement. There needs to be a simple statement(s) that show NAME, YEARS LEFT TO RETIREMENT, HOW MUCH NEEDS TO BE SAVED TO REACH RETIREMENT SAVINGS GOAL"""

"""Full Name"""
name = input("Enter your Full Name: ")

"""Current Age"""
currentAge = int(input("Enter your Current Age: "))

"""Desired Retirment Age"""
desiredRetirementage = int(input("Enter your desired Retirement Age: "))

"""Current Level of Retirement Savings"""
currentSavings = int(input("Enter your current level of Retirement Savings: "))

"""What is the Total Amount of Retirment Savings Is Needed at Retirement"""
retirementGoal = int(input("Enter your Retirement Savings Goal: "))

"""Years left until retirement"""
remainingYears = desiredRetirementage - currentAge

"""Earnings Needed to Retire"""
remainingSavings = retirementGoal - currentSavings

"""Verify Inputs"""
print(" ")
print("Inputs Summary. You Chose: ")
print("Full Name: ", name)
print("Current Age: ", currentAge)
print("Desired Retirement Age: ", desiredRetirementage)
print("Current Savings: ", currentSavings)
print("Retirment Goal: ", retirementGoal)
"""print(remainingYears)
print(remainingSavings)"""

"""Output with Name, Years until Retirement, and Needed Saving until retirement goal is reached
print(" ")
print("Your Results: ")
print("Name: ", name)
print("Years remaining until retirement: ", remainingYears)
print("Remaining Savings Goal: ", remainingSavings)"""

"""Statement"""
print(" ")
print(name)
print("You have", remainingYears, "years until you are ready to retire.", "In order to reach your retirement goal, you will need to save", remainingSavings, "USD.")

